                                    }
                                ],
                                "classes": []
                            }
                        ],
                        "text": "The penanggalan inserts their entrails into their humanoid body, allowing them to appear as and move about like a normal human. The body has 10 Hit Points and the same defenses as the penanggalan. When the body is destroyed, the penanggalan is ejected unharmed. The body becomes a corpse, and if it's neither controlled by the penanggalan nor stored in an alchemical vat, it decays as normal."
